IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. ADD-NUMBERS.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 NUM1          PIC 9(4) VALUE 25.
01 NUM2          PIC 9(4) VALUE 17.
01 RESULT        PIC 9(5).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    COMPUTE RESULT = NUM1 + NUM2
    DISPLAY "The sum of " NUM1 " and " NUM2 " is " RESULT
    STOP RUN.
